  <p>The written assignments in this module ask for your analysis, your interpretation, and your evaluative judgment. These come from you: from your training, your weeks of following a specific beat, and your capacity to bring specific knowledge to bear on specific evidence. AI tools cannot do this work because they do not have your beat, your training, or your ten weeks of attention. If you use AI tools at any point in your writing process, disclose it specifically: which tool, what for, and how you verified the output. Undisclosed AI use in graded work is a violation of academic integrity in this course.</p>
