<div class="page-rule"></div>
<div class="block">
  <h3>Purpose</h3>
  <p>The Story Arc Analysis asks you to make an argument about structure, not about the events your beat covers. How did coverage develop? What drove the turning points? Who spoke and who was absent? What pattern in the coverage system becomes visible when you watch it for four weeks? The central deliverable is one arguable analytical claim, supported by specific evidence from your beat work across four weeks.</p>
